text: Guisan may refer to: * 1960 Guisan, a main-belt asteroid named after Henri Guisan * General-Guisan-Quai, a section of the Zürich quays named after Henri Guisan * Hélène Guisan (born 1916), Swiss author * Henri Guisan (1874–1960], a politician and popular military person of Switzerland * Jean Samuel Guisan (1740-1801), a Swiss engineer
title: Guisan
